# Alpha Brand Rules — Official Reference

## Official Logo

Always use the approved logo asset: `src/assets/alpha-logo.png` via `AlphaOfficialLogo` from `@/components/brand`.

The logo image already contains: gold symbol, ALPHA, and ✠ ⲀⲖⲈⲪⲀ ✠.

**Never** re-type ALPHA or ✠ ⲀⲖⲈⲪⲀ ✠ below the logo.
**Never** redesign, recreate, or substitute with icons or similar fonts.

## Official Slogan

The only approved slogan (literal, unchanged):

`Ⲁ ————THE COPTIC ORTHODOX DIGITAL HOME ————Ⲱ`

Use `ALPHA_OFFICIAL_SLOGAN` from `@/components/brand`.

Do not replace with Welcome To Alpha, Start Your Journey, or any other text.

## Brand Header Pattern

When full identity is required (Church Setup, login, signup, brand headers):

1. `AlphaOfficialLogo` or `AlphaBrandIdentity`
2. Official slogan
3. Page title (e.g. طلب تأسيس كنيسة)

Use `AlphaBrandHeader` or `ProfileSubShell` with `brand` prop.

## Visual Style

Premium Gold · Luxury Gold Gradient · Soft Glow · Coptic Orthodox Identity · Warm Beige Background
